{"data":{"id":"ChIJb-HkRuRYwokRF5qsEyxejyc","rating":4.9,"websiteUri":"https://www.209nycdental.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=gmb","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":false,"periods":[{"open":{"day":0,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":0,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":1,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":1,"hour":18,"minute":30}},{"open":{"day":2,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":2,"hour":18,"minute":30}},{"open":{"day":3,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":3,"hour":18,"minute":30}},{"open":{"day":4,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":4,"hour":18,"minute":30}},{"open":{"day":5,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":5,"hour":17,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":6,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":6,"hour":15,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: 7:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 7:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 7:30 AM – 3:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM"],"nextOpenTime":"2026-02-17T12:30:00Z"},"userRatingCount":1762,"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJb-HkRuRYwokRF5qsEyxejyc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsTVNFRlpORWgxYWxBM1VWUkJNalZFYzE5UmFIYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Highly recommend this office.\nDainea, the treatment coordinator, was absolutely amazing from the very beginning. She went out of her way to help me secure an appointment before the end of the year so I could maximize my insurance benefits, which I truly appreciated. She was organized, responsive, and made the entire scheduling process completely stress-free.\nDr. Reddy is one of the kindest and most gentle dentists I’ve ever met. She took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire visit. I honestly didn’t feel the injection at all, which says so much about her skill and gentle approach. The procedure itself was quick, smooth, and completely painless, and I felt at ease the whole time.\nFrom start to finish, the entire team made me feel cared for and comfortable. This was hands down the best dental experience I’ve ever had, and I would highly recommend this dental office to anyone looking for exceptional care.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Highly recommend this office.\nDainea, the treatment coordinator, was absolutely amazing from the very beginning. She went out of her way to help me secure an appointment before the end of the year so I could maximize my insurance benefits, which I truly appreciated. She was organized, responsive, and made the entire scheduling process completely stress-free.\nDr. Reddy is one of the kindest and most gentle dentists I’ve ever met. She took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire visit. I honestly didn’t feel the injection at all, which says so much about her skill and gentle approach. The procedure itself was quick, smooth, and completely painless, and I felt at ease the whole time.\nFrom start to finish, the entire team made me feel cared for and comfortable. This was hands down the best dental experience I’ve ever had, and I would highly recommend this dental office to anyone looking for exceptional care.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"DeJuan Bailey","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103047182129586894509/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOSlklzOy33y943kKmHQN_kMgFWX5uApWQqrhQus6jYJTb2w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-05T23:29:56.059181899Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsTVNFRlpORWgxYWxBM1VWUkJNalZFYzE5UmFIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsTVNFRlpORWgxYWxBM1VWUkJNalZFYzE5UmFIYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c258e446e4e16f:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17"},{"name":"places/ChIJb-HkRuRYwokRF5qsEyxejyc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pac2RtWlJWVUZIWWxSRlFVMXZWbDlZYTA5UE1YYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 weeks ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"The staff are always hospitable. Simple and easy check ins. They remind you of your upcoming appointments via text, email and call based on preferences. All dentist assistants are very caring and efficient. The doctor's office is in a residential building, space is clean, and bright but very welcoming. I came across this dentist because I had a tooth ache a little over a year ago and I've been back ever since.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"The staff are always hospitable. Simple and easy check ins. They remind you of your upcoming appointments via text, email and call based on preferences. All dentist assistants are very caring and efficient. The doctor's office is in a residential building, space is clean, and bright but very welcoming. I came across this dentist because I had a tooth ache a little over a year ago and I've been back ever since.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Tiffany Watson","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103886977165458326863/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdgX7a25ldz3s3EFd-PpL6_x7LOi4UH0GpUELjXJQ-HuBudnVEuA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-29T02:23:37.748516120Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pac2RtWlJWVUZIWWxSRlFVMXZWbDlZYTA5UE1YYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pac2RtWlJWVUZIWWxSRlFVMXZWbDlZYTA5UE1YYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c258e446e4e16f:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17"},{"name":"places/ChIJb-HkRuRYwokRF5qsEyxejyc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pScFNrbE9aVXd3VjJocExXSXlWV3g0UlhGV1RIYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 weeks ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I saw the hygenist Jun Chen and Dr. Dmitry today and they were both great. I had really bad staining in my front tooth and Jun was able to make my teeth look like it belongs in a hollywood set.\n\n5 stars for the entire experience. I felt like I was in good hands and would 100% recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I saw the hygenist Jun Chen and Dr. Dmitry today and they were both great. I had really bad staining in my front tooth and Jun was able to make my teeth look like it belongs in a hollywood set.\n\n5 stars for the entire experience. I felt like I was in good hands and would 100% recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Chai Cheng","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102638954666497893365/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJQU3Q123-qpJGY_XlkEBA5v1R9vQ3srGvrV7Mnfxqxafs1w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-31T19:01:04.595599838Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pScFNrbE9aVXd3VjJocExXSXlWV3g0UlhGV1RIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pScFNrbE9aVXd3VjJocExXSXlWV3g0UlhGV1RIYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c258e446e4e16f:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17"},{"name":"places/ChIJb-HkRuRYwokRF5qsEyxejyc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paZlRUSmhPRWs0YWt4TVNXbG9ObmgxVjBwSU1tYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"A great visit overall! The X-ray technician was very friendly, and I appreciated his gentle approach to placing the things in my mouth. Aaron is a great hygienist and did a very thorough cleaning. Also very friendly. I appreciated the scan that Dr. Yasmika did and how she explained everything to me on the screen. The only area of improvement I would mention is that there was a bit of wait times between each thing.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"A great visit overall! The X-ray technician was very friendly, and I appreciated his gentle approach to placing the things in my mouth. Aaron is a great hygienist and did a very thorough cleaning. Also very friendly. I appreciated the scan that Dr. Yasmika did and how she explained everything to me on the screen. The only area of improvement I would mention is that there was a bit of wait times between each thing.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Jesse Robbins","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114576756746052903210/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqzm0vHxJAW6k55yZM1aCFdeDO92dWv6HtEh_rQoE1JmTflXc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2026-01-12T21:57:58.810169757Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paZlRUSmhPRWs0YWt4TVNXbG9ObmgxVjBwSU1tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paZlRUSmhPRWs0YWt4TVNXbG9ObmgxVjBwSU1tYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c258e446e4e16f:0x278f5e2c13ac9a17"},{"name":"places/ChIJb-HkRuRYwokRF5qsEyxejyc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxNFFVTlVaa1ZFTjJJNFJIbHdXV2N3ZFVoVVVsRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I came in after a few years of neglecting my teeth, and was met with the most kind, patient, and understanding care I’ve ever experienced. Reception, hygienists—everybody at 209 Dental is incredible! I don’t think anybody loves going to the dentist, but I truthfully look forward to every appointment with Dr. Stella Park because I know the standard of care will exceed my expectations. Thank you so much!!! I love my smile!!!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I came in after a few years of neglecting my teeth, and was met with the most kind, patient, and understanding care I’ve ever experienced. Reception, hygienists—everybody at 209 Dental is incredible! I don’t think anybody loves going to the dentist, but I truthfully look forward to every appointment with Dr. Stella Park because I know the standard of care will exceed my expectations. Thank 